    else
    if ( list.Length == 1 )
      yourProcessID = list[0].Id;
    else
      Console.WriteLine($&quot;There is more than one &#39;notepad&#39; running : {list.Length} found.&quot;);

We get the list of running processes having the name `notepad`.

Then we check the count items found and manage it as indicated by the code.

We set `yourProcessID = -1` to indicates not found by default.

So if several notepad are found, you must decide what to do...

